Debianised by Steve Haslam, <araqnid@debian.org>, then maintained by
Zephaniah E. Hull <warp@debian.org>.

Currently maintained by Guillem Jover <guillem@debian.org>.

Originally from: <http://linux.3dfx.com/>
It was downloaded from <http://sf.net/projects/glide/>

The debian packages are maintained through Subversion on:

   <svn://svn.debian.org/pkg-device3dfx/>

This module is GPL, viz.:

